      • map

        public <T> T map(Class<T> mapper)
        Provides data mappers for further usage. If the given class is not annotated with Mapper or the model of the mapper can not be found, an JPersisException is thrown.
        Type Parameters:
        T - class type
        Parameters:
        mapper - given class or interface of a mapper
        Returns:
        mapper instance of the given class or interface
